Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:43.06,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:13.15,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:16.88,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:26.89,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:48.11,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:01.46,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've obtained the Fortune Arcana with your newest bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You are truly magnificent to have acquired so many new powers, one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Only another heart can penetrate into the depths of one's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is Narukami Yu if you multiply it by Margaret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hearts will—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I forgot to multiply myself by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was merely testing your level of understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations. You passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back! I'm the unlucky ninja, Mr. Experiment!{on TV}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You drink coffee, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.11,0:02:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When I got married, I promised her mother that the least I could do was make the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's become a bit of a habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink up while it's still hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, can you read to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, what book?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I've got work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not make it back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A hit-and-run near Samegawa, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, didn't your wife pass away in a car accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a bandage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a picture of Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from when we went to Samegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy put away all of our pictures of Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He did that right after she died in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about it since Daddy won't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'd get angry if I kept this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask him for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Daddy since he lost Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he feels the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I think so too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you too, Big Bro.{HNNNNG}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did God have to create tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? Let's just get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, I want a melon soda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go buy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get me one, I'll let you borrow the notes I copied from Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, couldn't I just borrow them from her in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She has better handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nanako's with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She made plans with Teddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting, Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A bear-y good day to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A bear-y good day to you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana, let's go on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a present if you get the highest test score.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm so jealous of Teddie right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start off with trigonometric identities.{sin^2 + cos^2 = 1. DONE}{8thsin has a trigonometric identity}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The real you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I still don't know who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My memories start with me living in that other world, not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might've been someone special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But then things started getting weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's when I ran into everyone and asked for their help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I came to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, do you get what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I bet you're a king!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I read in a book that a bad guy cursed the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so he had to wander through the forest alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, that could be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you break the spell soon, Teddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I stumbled upon this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako seems to really like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so could we leave it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you know her better than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Daddy, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Today at school, I got a...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My tummy really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it something you ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:08:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottom of my tummy feels all prickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What? We should call a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait. Hasn't this happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it feel like that one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap... I think I put that medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Who's calling now?!{WHY AT A TIME LIKE THIS?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Dojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi? I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A sealed letter? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it from Mr. Ichihara? When did it arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For the love of God— I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,there should be some medicine in the first aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Pen-Pen the baby penguin overcame many obstacles to return home.{background?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}He was greeted by a touching reunion with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,my real father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that maybe I'm not Daddy's real daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because bad people are more important to Daddy than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just today he rushed out and left me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They passed it out at school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher told us to give it to our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He said to put down when they could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But Daddy has work,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so he can't go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask him when he gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron! "I don't know" doesn't cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a detective's duty to do whatever it takes to solve a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dojima should be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Dojima never lets up, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he like that at home too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't convinced the kid's the serial killer, so he's doing his own research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, he's going nuts over the recent hit-and-run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! Gotta get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the change of clothes you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for a parent-teacher conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They need to know when you could make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fill it out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be coming home tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Nanako doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's feeling better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten since lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are the two orders for takeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,about Chisato's accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, I got a call from my old mentor, Mr. Ichihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for his help on a hit-and-run case, and his results just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a white sedan, probably American.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any cars like that around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Records indicate that it wasn't taken in to get scrapped or repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:12:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see, there was a similar accident last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The initial investigation we're currently conducting is critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you told Nanako anything about the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisato was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisato was hit on her way to pick up Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a cold day, and there weren't any witnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so no one found her until it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time word reached me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako had been stuck waiting at the preschool all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She was all alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for someone who would never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell Nanako that her mother had been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to catch the criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't have a single clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I {\i1}will{\i0} catch the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should stay with Nanako when she's sick—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:12:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do {\i1}you{\i0} know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, where's that paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Daddy fill it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he said whenever would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! Daddy's going to come?{inb4 he doesn't}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! This is my first parent-teacher conference!{classroom observation, but... that's just stupid}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says their parents are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I framed that picture we found yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens after you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to a place called Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! So Mom went to Heaven, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:14:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be watching over you during your conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'll go to Heaven when I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I see Mom if I went there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a long way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I wanna see Mom, though.{DUN DUN DUN}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an accident around Samegawa about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you look into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding old newspaper articles on it should be a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The hit-and-run incident in Inaba.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.61,0:14:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim was a woman who lived in town named Dojima Chisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Nanako's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I vaguely remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,People in town talked about it a bit at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they catch the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,According to this article, the police are still investigating the case,{according to the article? isn't that shit a year old?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're severely lacking information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll have a hard time solving this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never forgive the creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good ever comes from running! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle's a detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so this must be eating at him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookie, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I put Mom's picture here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, do you remember this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from when we went to Samegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, about coming to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, where's the form?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She means the form I gave you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure "whenever" is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since I'll never make it there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I can't afford to go when I'm so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Those bad guys are more important to you than I am, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it! Just forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's gotten into her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako was looking forward to you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That was cruel of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do? I've got work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try paying more attention to Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you actually told her about the hit-and-run...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What hit-and-run?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you never listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}never{\i0} do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, you're stupid! Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you call your father stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you care about me, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate me, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't "real."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't my real dad!{;_;}{might be worth rewriting this to be more easily splittable?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search for her in the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:18:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll try Junes. I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't find her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Has she mentioned anything to you lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Like somewhere she'd like to visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...{shorten this line if you can}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'll go to Heaven when I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I see Mom if I went there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's headed for Samegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisato, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,protect Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God you found her.{don't forget to remove this Christian Propaganda or dark_sage will get mad}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you're the family member she trusts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's more likely to listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still running from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako needs a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is where you've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When Mom was still with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you, me, and Mom came here to pick flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,just the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... Why did she leave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I want to see Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Daddy, did you forget about Mom?{split?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You hid all of her pictures, and you never talk about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hate me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always making you feel so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been lonely since Mom died,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I bet Daddy has been lonely too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I won't cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to work hard to cover for Mom so Daddy won't get lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good girl, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, let's work hard together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a special day for us as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a special day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:22:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the day when you, me, and Yu become a family.{you and yu}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What about before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, this is the day we become a real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... I don't really get it, but isn't that great, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, this cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,From today on, that's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use it. I'm sure it would make Chisato happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treasure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And before I forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Any day is" something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "Anytime's okay." I promise I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Families are meant to laugh, cry, and bicker...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They spend most of their long lives together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're supposed to be warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:22:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.43,0:23:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I was avoiding that by chasing someone who had run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who made me realize that, Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it because we're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to continue pursuing the culprit who hit Chisato,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but I won't use that as an excuse to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it because I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, this is my town.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's special to me since it's where you and Nanako live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I am going to continue protecting this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it as both a detective and as a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.47,0:24:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "beauty pageant"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.14,0:24:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out our group date café...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I look stupid, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.06,0:24:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you too, Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.61,0:24:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.86,0:24:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'll take one.
